Larry is a client living in Falador and is involved in the Mahogany Homes activity. He is one of the possible NPCs that the player can be tasked with helping.

Construction contracts[edit | edit source]

Larry is a possible client given to the player by Mahogany Homes, and may ask you to build the following furniture for them, depending on the type of contract that player chose:

Furniture Resources Experience
Drawers (1) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Drawers (2) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Grandfather Clock 1 plank 127.5 160 190 240
Hat stand 1 plank 127.5 160 190 240
Table (1) 3 planks 67.5 144 216 336
Table (2) 3 planks 67.5 144 216 336
Range 1 steel bar 120 120 120 120
